==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Primitively
<hw>Prim"i*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Originally; at
first.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Primarily; not derivatively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>According to the original rule or ancient practice;
in the ancient style.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Primitiveness</ent>⟦br⟧
